    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable entry into car ownership or a rewarding weekend project? This vehicle is in poor condition and will require some mechanical and cosmetic work, but it offers a great foundation for someone who loves to bring a car back to life! It's a budget-friendly opportunity for a handy buyer looking for a diamond in the rough.",
